tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_medical_records (
  patient_id INT,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255),
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  dob DATE,
  test_result_id INT,
  test_type VARCHAR(50),
  test_date DATE,
  test_result TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE patient_medical_records (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender CHAR(1),
  blood_type VARCHAR(5)
);

CREATE TABLE genetic_test_results (
  test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  test_date DATE,
  test_result TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patient_medical_records(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  dob DATE NOT NULL,
  gender VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
  ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
  diagnosis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE genetic_tests (
  test_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT REFERENCES patients(patient_id),
  test_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  test_date DATE NOT NULL,
  result TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  address TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE MedicalRecords (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  date_of_visit DATE,
  diagnosis TEXT,
  prescription TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE GeneticTests (
  test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  test_date DATE,
  test_result TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ResearchData (
  research_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  research_topic TEXT,
  research_description TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255),
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  blood_type VARCHAR(5)
)

CREATE TABLE MedicalRecords (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  diagnosis VARCHAR(255),
  prescription VARCHAR(255),
  record_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE GeneticTests (
  test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  test_type VARCHAR(50),
  test_result TEXT,
  test_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Doctors (
  doctor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  doctor_name VARCHAR(255),
  specialty VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Clinics (
  clinic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  clinic_name VARCHAR(255),
  location VARCHAR(255)
)
